snippet.title: Aukaat Ke Bahar - Official Trailer ft. Elvish Yadav, Nikhil Vijay, Malhaar Rathod | Amazon MX Player
snippet.description:
Amazon MX Player presents 
Aukaat Ke Bahar - Official Trailer

Starring: Elvish Yadav, Malhaar Rathod, Nikhil Vijay, Hetal Gada, Rohan Khurrana, Keshav Sadhna
Production House: Rusk Studios
Produced By: Rusk Media Pvt. Ltd.
Directed By: Tanmai Rastogi
Developed, Story, Screenplay and Written by: Jayati Pandya, Akhilesh Vats, Jasmeet Bhatia, Ayush Gaur, Sumbul Khan, Siddharth Saini

Genre: Drama Romance
 
About Aukaat Ke Bahar: Rajveer Ahlawat, a small-town boxer from Safidon, enters DelhiтАЩs elite St. Collins college to fulfill his brotherтАЩs dream of becoming a polished, English-speaking graduate. Amidst bullies, culture shocks, and class divides, he falls for Antara Shukla тАФ a senior with political aspirations and far out of his league. When a humiliating dare collides with his growing feelings and a family crisis back home, Rajveer must fight harder than ever тАФ this time, not for glory, but for love, dignity, and survival.

About Amazon MX Player
Amazon MX Player is IndiaтАЩs leading free, premium, ad-supported entertainment service in India. It offers a diverse range of award-winning web series, reality shows, popular international shows, and a massive movie library across multiple genres. With a strong focus on original content, Amazon MX Player has launched some of the largest shows in India, which includes Ek Badnaam Aashram, Campus Diaries, Jamnapaar, Half CA, Bhaukaal, Raktanchal, Dehati Ladke, WhoтАЩs your Gynac, Sixer, Hip Hop India, Hunter тАУ Totega Nahi Todega and more. Amazon MX Player also offers a rich selection of international content dubbed in Hindi, Tamil, and Telugu under MX Vdesi, featuring popular shows like What's Wrong With Secretary Kim?, Daydreamer, Gangnam Beauty, My Girlfriend Is An Alien, Put Your Head On My Shoulder, Our Story, and more!

Ketika sebuah tantangan yang memalukan berbenturan dengan perasaannya yang semakin kuat dan krisis keluarga di kampung halaman, Rajveer harus berjuang lebih keras dari sebelumnya тАФ kali ini, bukan demi kejayaan, melainkan demi cinta, martabat, dan kelangsungan hidup.

Tentang Amazon MX Player
Amazon MX Player adalah layanan hiburan gratis, premium, dan beriklan terkemuka di India. Layanan ini menawarkan beragam serial web pemenang penghargaan, acara realitas, acara internasional populer, dan koleksi film yang sangat banyak dari berbagai genre. Dengan fokus yang kuat pada konten orisinal, Amazon MX Player telah meluncurkan beberapa acara terbesar di India, termasuk Ek Badnaam Aashram, Campus Diaries, Jamnapaar, Half CA, Bhaukaal, Raktanchal, Dehati Ladke, WhoтАЩs your Gynac, Sixer, Hip Hop India, Hunter тАУ Totega Nahi Todega, dan banyak lagi. Will Eleven get another chance at defeating Vecna? Is Max going to wake up? Can Will ever find peace in his life? These were just some of my biggest questions going into Stranger Things season 5, Volume 1. Seeing as it has been over three years since Stranger Things season 4's ending, my list of lingering questions has become overwhelmingly long. But I guess good things do come to those who wait, because Volume 1's four episodes quickly answer some of my most burning questions.

Set a year and a half after the events of season 4, Stranger Things season 5 finds Hawkins under military control following the "earthquake" that tore apart the town, which was actually caused by Vecna. The villain hasn't been seen since he was thrown from a window with a shotgun blast, but that hasn't stopped the group from staying ready for Vecna's next move. Sung by the dynamic duo Khesari Lal Yadav and Priyanka Singh, this love track beautifully captures the essence of romance through heartfelt lyrics and soulful melodies. With its catchy composition and visually stunning official video, this Bhojpuri DJ song is quickly becoming a fan favorite across social media and music platforms.

The music video showcases a compelling love story blending traditional Bhojpuri vibes with a modern cinematic touch. Whether you're a fan of Bhojpuri cinema, love songs, or the chart-topping voice of Khesari Lal Yadav, "Disco Mein Kisko Nachaogi" is a must-watch and a must-listen.

Presenting the second single "Ratnamala" from 'Parasakthi' starring Sivakarthikeyan, Ravi Mohan, Atharvaa, Sreeleela and others. Directed by Sudha Kongara. Music Composed by G.V. Prakash Kumar.

Music by G. V. Prakash Kumar

Lyrics: 
Pallavi 
Ratnamalaa !! Ratnamala !!  
Nannu veedi nuvvala poraadhey.  
Ratnamalaa !! Ratnamala !!  
Minnu veedi vennela poraadhey  
Ulagame suzhalvadhean? 
Udhiriyaai udaivadhean? 
yetho noolondril varaindha 
Kurippu poley tholaindheneyтАж 
Ratna Malaa, Ratna Malaa 
Ennai vittu needhaan neengaadhey 
Ratna Malaa, Ratna Malaa 
Kannai vittu imaigal neengaadheyтАж 

Chorus 
Vaalai Kumari penne 
Vandhaan Kumaran ponne 
Solai pookkalin munne 
Olai vidu thoodhu kanne 

Chorus 
Nenjam adhu enna kallo 
Manjam ini aagum mullo 
Vanjam seyvaalo paavai 
Thanjam adhu undhan paadhai (paavai) 

Charanam 1 
Oh.. Oh.. Adiye neeyum nalamaa? 
Kadidham solli vidumaa? 
Meiyodu mutham kalandhuvaithathai 
En aasai solla vaarthai theerndhadhaiтАж 
Un pirivil nagal nogudhey 
En paruvam madal yerudhey 
Pen uruvam nizhalaanadhe 
Mei sera, maaneтАж! 

Chorus 
Vaalai Kumari penne 
Vandhaan Kumaran ponne 
Solai pookkalin munne 
Olai vidu thoodhu kanne 

Chorus 
Nenjam adhu enna kallo 
Manjam ini aagum mullo 
Vanjam seyvaalo paavai 
Thanjam adhu undhan paadhai (paavai) 

Pallavi Repeat 
Ratna Malaa, Ratna Malaa 
Kannai vittu imaigal neengaadheyтАж 

Charanam 2 
Oh.. Oh.. AzhageтАж idhazh oram, melidhaai 
Muruval koodum 
Karum mega kootil minnal keetru polтАж 
Araipulli yodu neelum paattai polтАж 
Viral idukkin peana munai 
Idam maatru neeyum adhaiтАж 
Un meani theendidum vaira 
Madalthaalum naaneтАж 

Pallavi Final 
Ulagame suzhalvadhean? 
Udhiriyaai udaivadhean? 
yetho noolondril varaindha 
Kurippu poley tholaindheneyтАж 
Ratna Malaa, Ratna Malaa 
Ennai vittu needhaan neengaadhey 
Ratna Malaa, Ratna Malaa 
Kannai vittu imaigal neengaadheyтАж

ЁЯСЗ ╫С╫б╫и╫Ш╫Х╫Я ╫Ф╫Ц╫Ф: ╫Р╫а╫Ч╫а╫Х ╫Ю╫Ч╫д╫й╫Щ╫Э ╫Р╫к ╫Ф╫з╫Ь╫д╫Щ╫Э ╫Ф╫Щ╫з╫и╫Щ╫Э ╫Х╫Ф╫Р╫Щ╫Ь╫Щ╫Ш╫Щ╫Щ╫Э ╫С╫Щ╫Х╫к╫и ╫С╫Ю╫й╫Ч╫з. ╫ж╫д╫Х ╫Ы╫й╫Р╫а╫Щ ╫Ю╫д╫и╫Ш ╫Р╫к ╫Ф╫в╫Ь╫Х╫Щ╫Х╫к ╫Х╫д╫Х╫к╫Ч ╫Ч╫С╫Щ╫Ь╫Х╫к ╫Ь╫Р╫Т╫У╫Х╫к ╫Ы╫Ю╫Х ╫и╫Х╫а╫Р╫Ь╫У╫Х ╫а╫Ц╫Р╫и╫Щ╫Х (R9), ╫Ц╫Щ╫а╫У╫Щ╫Я ╫Ц╫Щ╫У╫Р╫Я, ╫У╫Щ╫Х╫Х╫Щ╫У ╫С╫з╫Ф╫Р╫Э ╫Х╫Р╫Щ╫з╫и ╫з╫б╫Щ╫Р╫б.

ЁЯдп ╫Ю╫й╫Щ╫Ы╫Х╫к ╫Ю╫Ш╫Х╫и╫д╫Х╫к: ╫Р╫к╫Э ╫Ь╫Р ╫к╫Р╫Ю╫Щ╫а╫Х ╫Р╫Щ╫Ц╫Ф ╫Ю╫Ц╫Ь ╫Щ╫й ╫Ф╫Щ╫Х╫Э! ╫Ф╫ж╫Ь╫Ч╫а╫Х ╫Ь╫Р╫и╫Х╫Ц:

115 OVR R9 ╫и╫Х╫а╫Р╫Ь╫У╫Х (╫Ф╫к╫Х╫д╫в╫Ф!)

115 OVR ╫и╫Х╫С╫и╫Ш╫Х ╫з╫и╫Ь╫Х╫б (╫Ш╫Щ╫и╫Х╫г ╫Ы╫д╫Х╫Ь!)

115 OVR ╫б╫Ш╫Щ╫С╫Я ╫Т'╫и╫Р╫и╫У ╫Х╫и╫Р╫Х╫Ь

113 OVR ╫Ц╫Ь╫Р╫Ш╫Я ╫Р╫Щ╫С╫и╫Ф╫Щ╫Ю╫Х╫С╫Щ╫е' ╫Х╫в╫Х╫У ╫и╫С╫Щ╫Э!

ЁЯСЗ уБУуБохЛХчФ╗уБохЖЕхо╣я╝ЪуВ▓уГ╝уГахЖЕуБзцЬАуВВщлШф╛буБзуВиуГкуГ╝уГИуБкуВлуГ╝уГЙуВТцОвуБЧц▒ВуВБуБ╛уБЩуАВф╛бца╝уВТхИЖцЮРуБЧуАБуГнуГКуВжуГЙуГ╗уГКуВ╢уГкуВкя╝ИR9я╝ЙуАБуВ╕уГНуГЗуВгуГ╝уГМуГ╗уВ╕уГАуГ│уАБуГЗуГУуГГуГЙуГ╗уГЩуГГуВлуГауАБуВдуВ▒уГлуГ╗уВлуВ╖уГ╝уВ╕уГгуВ╣уБиуБДуБгуБЯуГмуВ╕уВзуГ│уГЙщБ╕цЙЛуБоуГСуГГуВпуВТщЦЛуБСуВЛцзШхнРуВТуБФшжзуБПуБауБХуБДуАВ

ЁЯдп уБиуВУуБзуВВуБкуБДх╝ХуБНя╝Ъф╗КцЧеуБох╣╕щБЛуБпф┐буБШуВЙуВМуБкуБДуБ╗уБйуБзуБЩя╝Бф╗КхЫЮуАБф╗еф╕ЛуБощБ╕цЙЛуВТцПГуБИуБ╛уБЧуБЯя╝Б

OVR 115 уВ╖уВ░уГНуГБуГгуГ╝ уВ╕уГНуГЗуВгуГ╝уГМуГ╗уВ╕уГАуГ│я╝ИуГХуГйуГ│уВ╣уБощнФшбУх╕ля╝Бя╝Й

OVR 115 R9 уГнуГКуВжуГЙя╝ИщйЪчХ░уБощБ╕цЙЛя╝Бя╝Й

OVR 115 уГнуГЩуГлуГИуГ╗уВлуГлуГнуВ╣я╝ИуГАуГЦуГлуВжуВйуГ╝уВпуВвуВжуГИуГЮуГГуГЙуГНуВ╣я╝Бя╝Й

OVR 115 уВ╣уГЖуВгуГ╝уГЦуГ│уГ╗уВ╕уВзуГйуГ╝уГЙя╝ЖуГйуВжуГл

snippet.title: 4 AADMI (Official Music Video) | Sumit Parta | Mr.Maxxx | New Haryanvi Song 2025
snippet.description:
Mahra Tora presents the official music video of 4 Aadmi by Sumit Parta & Mr.Maxxx. It is a powerful Haryanvi track full of energy, emotion, and real-life hustle. 4 Aadmi celebrates confidence, struggle, and the moment when doubters finally start giving respect. ItтАЩs an anthem for every youngster chasing dreams and proving their worth through hard work.

ЁЯОз Listen to 4 Aadmi on all audio stores:-

Choro hada m bitha de chot
Bakri tu koni goat
Vair koni ghale yaar
Dekh k n kadi thoth
Jealousy na rakhu jadi
Moj me hi reu roj
Chahe khali ho ya bhari revo
Mero goj
Choro winner hai
Mehngo khave dinner hai
Part time punya kare
Full time sinner hai
Feelings inner hai
Rap game k mha
Choro jadu kre jiya witcher hai
Truth bitter hai
Log side switcher hai
Jo sath khaya piya be hi
Yaar sala snitcher hai
Dhue m uda ryo yaar sari fikar hai
Thadi mehfila me chale mero hi jikar hai
kon jle kon tle mera dhyan koni
Golibaji ala mne gyaan koni
Goli awe h chlani che bnda marwalo
Me normal banda bhgwan koni
Lagi jaat gail yaari aag dewe ge
Yaar Baniye b goli re chla dewe ge
Mehnga rakhna b howe  hatiyar lajmi
Mhari sangat me bnja khukhar admi
Re ghnta fark ni bole k ye 4 admi
Bs door rho pka me bekar admi
Khuli ankhya te hi dekhra hu bde sapne
Kad chain te tah soya mere khud yaad ni
Chiye range rover pura hangover
Nind kachi paki Chiye hot shawer
Ghadi Rm ki dhila dhila lower
Sale ve kiu chidee jo mne mile koni
mere personal kise gelya gile koni
Me to Bina dekhe mar deu  teer target pe
Ve Dhyan lake mare par pile konya
Re ghar k upar jhaj uda du

sir pe jonsa taj hta du

kisne dekhya kal re bete
Systam sara aj dikha du
